title: E86 Autopsies
itunes:title: Autopsies
description:
In this episode, the team discusses autopsies with forensic pathologist specialist and author of "The Handbook of Zombie Forensics and Medicine", Dr. Darin Wolfe.

Follow Dr. Darin Wolfe on Tiktok @the_dead_letter and on Instagram @anatomy_and_the_dead !

Make sure to check out Dr. Darin Wolfe's podcast "Knife After Death" on Youtube, Facebook, and wherever you listen to podcasts!

Go to JimJefferies.com to buy tickets to Jim's upcoming tour, The Moist Tour.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
